      *    END-IF.
      *

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND COCV6230-CEMPRESA NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CEMPRESA
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6230-CEMPRESA
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
                 THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL1000-CCOD-S      TO COCV6231-CEMPRESA-S
                 MOVE TGCL1000-CCOD-CAPLIC TO COCV6231-CEMPRESA-CAPLIC
